<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمُبْهَمَاتُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٤٨. وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُبْهَمُ الرُّوَاةِ»</span>: مَا لَمْ يُسْمَى … كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«امْرَأَةٍ»</span> فِي الْحَيْضِ وَهْيَ أَسْمَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٤٩. وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ رَقَى سَيِّدَ ذَاكَ الْحَيِّ»</span> … رَاقٍ أَبِي سَعِيدٍ الْخُدْرِيِّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩٥٠.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهُ نَحْوُ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ابْنِ فُلَانٍ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عَمِّهِ»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عَمَّتِهِ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«زَوْجَتِهِ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ابْنِ أُمِّهِ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>